  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978790/extras/bf404b324c51b47674a3c750b42caa42.poster.avif?t=1751659204\" width=588 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978790/extras/bf404b324c51b47674a3c750b42caa42.webm?t=1751659204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978790/extras/bf404b324c51b47674a3c750b42caa42.mp4?t=1751659204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978790/extras/0692fea656b2e12a2ae054d95876870c.avif?t=1751659204\" width=450 height=84 /></span><br>Naxos is like all of my other games!<br><br>I just feel like there arent many Auto Battle RPGS out there....<br><br>I really want to keep moving the genre forward!<br><br><br><br>Okay why not try even more different formulas??<br><br>This time I decided to not use big menus ==( Many houses) <br><br>I tried compacting everything in the game in 3 houses!<br><br>I also feel like the game is better to learn... By making things small...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978790/extras/bdb251ae291076eff9fd52d67742c37d.avif?t=1751659204\" width=450 height=84 /></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Craft equipment<br></li><li>Almost Endless Grind***<br></li><li>Academy(Abbilites to learn)<br></li><li>10 Different Scenarios<br></li><li>10 Unique Enemies<br></li><li>Automatic Progression<br></li><li>Mining!</li></ul>",
